data.description: Welcome to this single-family home located on the picturesque Space Coast of Florida! This spacious and beautifully designed residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and coastal living. As you step through the entrance, you're immediately greeted by an open floor plan. Livingroom area with accent wall and fireplace. One of the standout features of this home is the dual master suites. Both suites are generously sized, offering plenty of room for relaxation and rejuvenation. With the Space Coast as your backdrop, you'll have access to a myriad of recreational opportunities, from visiting the nearby Kennedy Space Center to enjoying the pristine beaches and water activities that the area is renowned for. This home offers not just a place to live, but a lifestyle to be savored.
